<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 items-center justify-center flex-col">
            <img class="h-48 mb-8 object-contain" src="/public/20251013_1025_PHI Peaceful Emblem.png" alt="PHI Logo">
            <div class="text-center lg:w-2/3 w-full">
                <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">About Peace Humanitarian Initiative</h1>
                <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">PHI is a non-governmental, non-profit organization dedicated to advancing peace, stability, and human development across Africa. Founded on the belief that peace and progress are inseparable, PHI works to empower communities affected by conflict, poverty, and social fragmentation. Our vision is an Africa where peace, dignity, and opportunity are shared by all.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto flex flex-wrap">
            <div class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full bg-gray-100 py-24 px-10 relative mb-4">
                    <img alt="Peaceful Community" class="w-full object-cover h-full object-center block opacity-25 absolute inset-0" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366754035-f200968a6e72?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80">
                    <div class="text-center relative z-10 w-full">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Our Core Pillars</h2>
                        <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">Guided by our vision of a peaceful and prosperous Africa, PHI's work is built upon three fundamental pillars that drive our mission forward.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-2">
                    <div class="px-2 w-full md:w-1/3 mb-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full bg-gray-100 sm:py-16 py-12 sm:px-8 px-6 relative h-full">
                            <img alt="Peacebuilding" class="w-full object-cover h-full object-center block opacity-25 absolute inset-0" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508182314998-3bd49475002f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80">
                            <div class="text-center relative z-10 w-full">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-3">Peacebuilding & Conflict Resolution</h2>
                                <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">Promoting dialogue, reconciliation, and social cohesion through community-based peace initiatives and conflict resolution programs.</p>
                                <a href="/programs/peacebuilding" class="mt-3 text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-2 w-full md:w-1/3 mb-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full bg-gray-100 sm:py-16 py-12 sm:px-8 px-6 relative h-full">
                            <img alt="Humanitarian Aid" class="w-full object-cover h-full object-center block opacity-25 absolute inset-0" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532629345422-7515f3d16bb6?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80">
                            <div class="text-center relative z-10 w-full">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-3">Humanitarian Relief & Recovery</h2>
                                <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">Delivering essential support and resources to communities affected by conflict, natural disasters, and humanitarian crises.</p>
                                <a href="/programs/humanitarian" class="mt-3 text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-2 w-full md:w-1/3 mb-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full bg-gray-100 sm:py-16 py-12 sm:px-8 px-6 relative h-full">
                            <img alt="Community Development" class="w-full object-cover h-full object-center block opacity-25 absolute inset-0" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3da57cac76a?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80">
                            <div class="text-center relative z-10 w-full">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-3">Sustainable Community Development</h2>
                                <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">Empowering communities through education, skills training, and sustainable development initiatives that create long-term opportunities.</p>
                                <a href="/programs/development" class="mt-3 text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR APPROACH</h2>
                <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">How We Make a Difference</h1>
                <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">At PHI, we believe in sustainable, community-driven solutions. Our approach combines local knowledge with global expertise to create lasting impact in the communities we serve across Africa.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap">
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Community Engagement</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">We work directly with local communities to understand their needs and co-create solutions that are culturally appropriate and sustainable.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Partnerships</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Collaborating with local organizations, governments, and international partners to maximize our impact and ensure sustainability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Innovation</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Leveraging technology and innovative approaches to solve complex challenges in peacebuilding and development.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Impact Measurement</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Rigorous monitoring and evaluation to ensure our programs deliver measurable, sustainable results.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
            <div class="xl:w-1/2 lg:w-3/4 w-full mx-auto text-center">
