                </svg>
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg">"PHI's commitment to sustainable peace and development has transformed our community. Their grassroots approach and deep understanding of local challenges have made a real difference in people's lives."</p>
                <span class="inline-block h-1 w-10 rounded bg-blue-500 mt-8 mb-6"></span>
                <h2 class="text-gray-900 font-medium title-font tracking-wider text-sm">AMINA JALLOH</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Community Leader, Sierra Leone</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

