            <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-widest">OUR TEAM</h1>
                <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Meet the dedicated individuals leading PHI's mission to create lasting peace and development across Africa. Our team combines local expertise with global perspectives to drive meaningful change.</p>
