                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 lg:w-1/2">
                    <div class="h-full flex sm:flex-row flex-col items-center sm:justify-start justify-center text-center sm:text-left">
                        <img alt="Field Coordinator" class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg w-48 h-48 object-cover object-center sm:mb-0 mb-4" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80">
                        <div class="flex-grow sm:pl-8">
                            <h2 class="title-font font-medium text-lg text-gray-900">Fatoumata Diallo</h2>
                            <h3 class="text-gray-500 mb-3">Field Operations Lead</h3>
                            <p class="mb-4">Fatoumata coordinates our on-the-ground efforts, working directly with local communities to implement and monitor PHI's programs.</p>
                            <span class="inline-flex">
                                <a class="text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-500">
                                    <svg fill="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 00-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 011-1h3z"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </a>
                                <a class="ml-3 text-gray-500 hover:text-pink-500">
